Packages that use com.tractrac.clientmodule
com.tractrac.clientmodule Main data classes related to an event's data.

com.tractrac.clientmodule.data.containers Classes that automatically receive and store different (event) data types. 
com.tractrac.clientmodule.setup Classes for setting up an event from a configuration source.
